[codex] We replicated Study 4A using feedback about the gender, rather than race, of authors initially selected for a local library reading list. Prior to this study, we conducted a pretest (N = 550) rating 21 candidate attributes on importance for gender (see Appendix Section S4 for full details). The three comparison attributes used did not differ significantly from gender on rated importance.
